### Local development requests — requires SPRING_PROFILES_ACTIVE=local
### H2 seed data: tenant-walmart-001 / camp-spring-sale-2024 / camp-abc-123
### Token is signed with JWT_SECRET=changeme and never expires (local use only)

@BASE_URL  = http://localhost:8080
@TOKEN     = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ0ZW5hbnRfaWQiOiJ0ZW5hbnQtd2FsbWFydC0wMDEiLCJzdWIiOiJsb2NhbC1kZXYiLCJleHAiOjk5OTk5OTk5OTl9.CIz4iP1G8wWahVxyJxd144jReFnn--VHelFAt7c5Ecs
@CAMPAIGN1 = camp-spring-sale-2024
@CAMPAIGN2 = camp-abc-123


### ── 1. HEALTH & ACTUATOR ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 1a. Liveness check — no token required
GET {{BASE_URL}}/actuator/health

###

### 1b. Prometheus metrics scrape
GET {{BASE_URL}}/actuator/prometheus


### ── 2. CLICKS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 2a. Today so far — defaults to midnight UTC → now (hits H2 seed rows)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN1}}/clicks
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 2b. Today so far — second seeded campaign
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN2}}/clicks
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 2c. With per-hour time series breakdown
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN1}}/clicks?timeSeries=true
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 2d. Explicit time range within today (realtime path — H2 returns data)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN1}}/clicks?start=2026-06-28T00:00:00Z&end=2026-06-28T23:59:59Z
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 2e. Historical range > 72h (historical path — H2 returns empty, routing verified)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN1}}/clicks?start=2026-06-01T00:00:00Z&end=2026-06-20T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}


### ── 3. IMPRESSIONS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 3a. Today so far
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN1}}/impressions
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 3b. Second campaign
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN2}}/impressions
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 3c. With time series
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN1}}/impressions?timeSeries=true
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}


### ── 4. CLICK-TO-BASKET ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 4a. Today so far
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN1}}/clickToBasket
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 4b. Second campaign
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN2}}/clickToBasket
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 4c. Explicit range
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN1}}/clickToBasket?start=2026-06-28T00:00:00Z&end=2026-06-28T23:59:59Z
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}


### ── 5. SWAGGER / OPENAPI ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 5a. Raw OpenAPI spec
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v3/api-docs
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 5b. Swagger UI (open in browser)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/swagger-ui/index.html
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}


### ── 6. ERROR SCENARIOS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 6a. No token → 401
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN1}}/clicks

###

### 6b. Invalid token → 401
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN1}}/clicks
Authorization: Bearer invalid.token.here

###

### 6c. Campaign not owned by tenant → 403
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/unknown-campaign-xyz/clicks
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 6d. start without end → 400
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN1}}/clicks?start=2026-06-28T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 6e. end before start → 400
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN1}}/clicks?start=2026-06-28T12:00:00Z&end=2026-06-28T06:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 6f. end equal to start → 400
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN1}}/clicks?start=2026-06-28T00:00:00Z&end=2026-06-28T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
